graph LR
    ODHNotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ODHNotebookController -->|watches same CR| KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller<br/>v0.0.0-20220728153354<br/>Creates StatefulSet]
    ODHNotebookController -->|creates ingress| OpenShiftRoute[OpenShift Route API<br/>route.openshift.io/v1<br/>External access]
    ODHNotebookController -->|reads config| OpenShiftConfig[OpenShift Config API<br/>config.openshift.io/v1<br/>Proxy configuration]
    ODHNotebookController -->|injects sidecar| OAuthProxy[OpenShift OAuth Proxy<br/>ose-oauth-proxy<br/>Authentication/Authorization]
    ODHNotebookController -->|requests certs| ServiceCA[Service CA Operator<br/>TLS provisioning<br/>via annotations]
    ODHNotebookController -->|API operations| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>v1.22+<br/>Core resources]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHNotebookController -.->|complementary controller| KubeflowController
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|creates Notebook CRs| ODHNotebookController
    ODHOperator[ODH Operator] -->|deploys & manages| ODHNotebookController

    %% Integration Points
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes /metrics| ODHNotebookController
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>OAuth 2.0<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    OAuthProxy -->|authorizes via SAR| K8sAPI

    %% External Services
    ODHNotebookController -->|pulls images| ContainerRegistry[Container Registries<br/>quay.io, registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    OAuthProxy -->|pulls image| ContainerRegistry

